---
const base = import.meta.env.BASE_URL.replace(/\/$/, '');
const year = new Date().getFullYear();
---
<footer class="mt-24 bg-ironbark text-chalk">
  {/* Acknowledgment of Country ribbon */}
  <div class="border-b border-chalk/10">
    <div class="wrap py-10 md:py-12 grid md:grid-cols-12 gap-8 items-start">
      <div class="md:col-span-3">
        <div class="font-mono uppercase tracking-wide2 text-[10px] text-ochre mb-2">Acknowledgment of Country</div>
        <div class="font-display text-2xl leading-tight">With respect.</div>
      </div>
      <p class="md:col-span-9 text-chalk/80 leading-relaxed text-[15px] max-w-3xl">
        Outback Pantry acknowledges the Arrernte people as the Traditional Custodians of the land on which our Alice Springs warehouse stands, and we pay our respects to Elders past and present. Every ingredient in this pantry has been harvested from Country under the guidance of the First Nations cooperatives we partner with. The knowledge behind this food is 60,000 years old. We are grateful to carry a small part of it to your kitchen.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="wrap py-16 grid md:grid-cols-12 gap-10">
    <div class="md:col-span-4">
      <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-5">
        <span class="relative w-11 h-11 border border-chalk/30 flex items-center justify-center rounded-full">
          <span class="font-display text-[22px] leading-none text-ochre">O</span>
          <span class="absolute -right-1 -top-1 w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-ochre"></span>
        </span>
        <div class="font-display text-lg">Outback Pantry</div>
      </div>
      <p class="text-chalk/70 text-sm leading-relaxed max-w-xs">
        A native-food grocer working with Indigenous-owned harvest cooperatives across the Northern Territory, Western Australia and the central desert. Settler-founded. Respectfully sourced.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="md:col-span-2">
      <h4 class="text-chalk text-xs font-mono uppercase tracking-wide2 text-ochre mb-4">Shop</h4>
      <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm">
        <li><a href={`${base}/pantry/#spice`} class="text-chalk/70 hover:text-ochre">Native Spices</a></li>
        <li><a href={`${base}/pantry/#fruit`} class="text-chalk/70 hover:text-ochre">Bush Fruits</a></li>
        <li><a href={`${base}/pantry/#seed`} class="text-chalk/70 hover:text-ochre">Seeds &amp; Grains</a></li>
        <li><a href={`${base}/pantry/#sauce`} class="text-chalk/70 hover:text-ochre">Sauces &amp; Condiments</a></li>
        <li><a href={`${base}/pantry/#hamper`} class="text-chalk/70 hover:text-ochre">Gift Hampers</a></li>
      </ul>
    </div>
    <div class="md:col-span-3">
      <h4 class="text-chalk text-xs font-mono uppercase tracking-wide2 text-ochre mb-4">Learn</h4>
      <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm">
        <li><a href={`${base}/stories/`} class="text-chalk/70 hover:text-ochre">Stories from the Bush</a></li>
        <li><a href={`${base}/harvest/`} class="text-chalk/70 hover:text-ochre">Our Harvest Network</a></li>
        <li><a href={`${base}/recipes/`} class="text-chalk/70 hover:text-ochre">Recipes</a></li>
        <li><a href={`${base}/about/`} class="text-chalk/70 hover:text-ochre">About Outback Pantry</a></li>
        <li><a href={`${base}/about/#trade`} class="text-chalk/70 hover:text-ochre">Restaurants &amp; Trade</a></li>
      </ul>
    </div>
    <div class="md:col-span-3">
      <h4 class="text-chalk text-xs font-mono uppercase tracking-wide2 text-ochre mb-4">Warehouse</h4>
      <address class="not-italic text-sm text-chalk/70 leading-relaxed">
        Outback Pantry HQ<br/>
        14 Stott Terrace<br/>
        Alice Springs NT 0870<br/>
        <span class="coord text-ochre/80 block mt-2">-23.698° / 133.881°</span>
        <a href="mailto:hello@outbackpantry.com.au" class="text-ochre hover:text-chalk block mt-3">hello@outbackpantry.com.au</a>
      </address>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="border-t border-chalk/10">
    <div class="wrap py-6 flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center justify-between gap-2 text-xs text-chalk/60">
      <span>&copy; {year} Outback Pantry Pty Ltd · ABN 61 204 118 049</span>
      <span class="font-mono uppercase tracking-wide2 text-[10px]">Harvested on Country · Shipped Australia-wide</span>
    </div>
  </div>
</footer>
